Iwe unozviziva izvi. Nei uri kundibvunza? Unoziva. Iwe hausi kuona chiedza kose-kose here?

0:05:21.820,0:05:22.520
Chiedza chacho chiripi?

0:05:22.520,0:05:24.040
Hausi kuchiona here?

0:05:24.040,0:05:30.540
Iwe urikuona nokuti une maziso mana - maziso chaiwo ne umweya saka urikuchiona.

0:05:30.540,0:05:37.260
Nei uri kundibvunza? Iwe haugone kuona chiedza che Munhu Akarurama kwose kwose here? Hausi kuchiona here?

0:05:37.260,0:05:39.640
Chiedza chiri kuita sei ku humambo hwako, iwe dhimoni?

0:05:39.640,0:05:44.440
Chiedza change chichikanganisa umambo hwangu.

