0:11:54.740,0:11:58.520
Vakandigadza korona ya vahosi zuva iroro.

0:11:58.520,0:12:04.200
Vakandipa masimba mumaziso angu, mumuromo ne muhudyu.

0:12:04.200,0:12:07.120
Chinhu chipi nechipi chandinotaura zvino se ...

