Pakazosvika 12 pakati pousiku, vakauya vakandiratidza vanhu vazhinji

0:13:21.200,0:13:29.660
munyika yezvomweya, vanhu vazhinji vakuru kuru, vakamirira kundigamuchira.

0:13:29.660,0:13:34.580
